Summary: 
    Elpis CRM is a web-based customer relationship management system built with an ASP.NET Core Web API backend and a React frontend.
It provides comprehensive contact and deal management, task and meeting scheduling, notes, product catalogs, bulk import/export, and dashboard reporting — designed for easy deployment and extension.
Use case: Ideal for small-to-medium businesses that need a lightweight, customizable CRM to track sales processes, customer interactions, and operational tasks.
Key Features

API-first:
Layered Controllers → Services → EF Core AppDbContext.
Contact & Deals: Full CRUD, relationships, and bulk operations.
Tasks & Meetings: Scheduling, notes, and activity tracking.
Import/Export: CSV/SQL utilities for data migration.
Security: Authentication, password reset flows, environment-based configs.
Dashboard & Forecasting: Targets and reporting endpoints.
